The Clean Air category in this web service includes layers illustrating the ecosystems and natural resources that filter air, the need or demand for clean air, the impacts associated with air quality, and factors that place stress on air quality. EnviroAtlas allows the user to interact with a web-based, easy-to-use, mapping application to view and analyze multiple ecosystem services for the conterminous United States.
